skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: western film trivia
des: Western film trivia is designed to be fun and to challenge people who love the western film genre. Use one of the example phrases to launch the game. After launching, you will be read five questions. In order to answer the question, say the number of the answer choice you think is correct. At the end of five questions, you will be given your score. If you would like to answer five more questions, say "new game." If not, say "Alexa, exit." I'll continue adding new questions, so you never get bored of playing! I hope you have fun and enjoy!
